    'Kandungan kurikulum dibahagikan kepada tiga bahagian berdasarkan kelompok tajuk atau mengikut kesesuaian bidang kajian disiplin berkenaan untuk mengisi tiga Semester, iaitu S1, S2 dan S3 dalam tempoh pengajian selama 1½ tahun.' => 'The content of the curriculum is divided into three parts based on the group of titles or according to the suitability of the field of study of the discipline to fill three Semesters, namely S1, S2 and S3 during the study period of 1½ years.',
    'Kolej Tingkatan 6' => 'Form 6 College',
