    'PENDIDIKAN TEKNIKAL DAN LATIHAN VOKASIONAL(TVET)' => 'TECHNICAL EDUCATION AND VOCATIONAL TRAINING (TVET)',
    'Maklumat Umum TVET' => 'TVET General Information',
    'Kolej Vokasional' => 'Vocational College',
    'Maklumat Umum TVET' => 'TVET General Information',
    'Apa itu TVET?' => 'What is TVET?',
    'TVET merupakan singkatan bagi Pendidikan dan Latihan Teknikal dan Vokasional. TVET adalah proses pendidikan dan latihan yang mempunyai hala tuju pekerjaan dengan penekanan utama terhadap amalan industri. Ia bertujuan untuk menghasilkan tenaga kerja yang kompeten dalam bidang-bidang yang tertentu. Skop TVET perlu berdasarkan standard pekerjaan yang diiktiraf, dengan penekanan kepada komponen praktikal, kemahiran psikomotor, dan pendedahan kepada latihan di industri.' => 'TVET stands for Technical and Vocational Education and Training. TVET is an education and training process that has a job orientation with a major emphasis on industry practice. It aims to produce a competent workforce in certain fields. The scope of TVET should be based on recognized occupational standards, with an emphasis on practical components, psychomotor skills, and exposure to industry training.',
    'Tujuan TVET diperkenalkan?' => 'The purpose of TVET was introduced?',
    'Tujuan TVET diperkenalkan adalah bagi memenuhi permintaan industri dan menyumbang kepada pertumbuhan ekonomi, selaras dengan globalisasi, ekonomi berasaskan pengetahuan, kemajuan teknologi, dan mobiliti tenaga kerja global. TVET dengan mengupayakan pendekatan yang diterajui industri adalah penting untuk menyediakan modal insan berkemahiran yang diperlukan industri, terutama untuk menyokong peralihan sektor ekonomi ke arah aktiviti berasaskan pengetahuan, selari dengan aspirasi menjadi negara maju pada tahun 2020.' => 'The purpose of TVET was introduced to meet industry demand and contribute to economic growth, in line with globalization, knowledge-based economy, technological advancement, and global workforce mobility. TVET by pursuing an industry-led approach is important to provide the skilled human capital needed by the industry, especially to support the transition of the economic sector towards knowledge-based activities, in line with the aspiration of becoming a developed country in 2020.',
    'Agensi dan institusi yang terlibat dengan TVET?' => 'Agencies and institutions involved with TVET?',
    'Dua institusi TVET awam telah ditubuhkan pada tahun 1964 untuk menyediakan latihan kemahiran kepada belia, iaitu Institut Kemahiran Belia dan Negara (IKBN) Dusun Tua dan Institut Latihan Perindustrian (ILP) Kuala Lumpur. Kini lebih daripada 500 institusi TVET awam yang menawarkan pelbagai program TVET bagi semua peringkat pendidikan.' => 'Two public TVET institutions were established in 1964 to provide skills training to youth, namely the Dusun Tua Youth and National Skills Institute (IKBN) and the Kuala Lumpur Industrial Training Institute (ILP). There are now more than 500 public TVET institutions that offer a variety of TVET programs for all levels of education.',
    'Kumpulan / Tumpuan sasaran TVET?' => 'Target group / Focus of TVET?',
    'Secara umumnya, terdapat dua laluan untuk memasuki bidang TVET iaitu menerusi Sijil Pelajaran Malaysia (SPM) atau Pentaksiran Tingkatan 3 (PT3). Lepasan SPM berpeluang untuk melanjutkan pelajaran sama ada dalam bidang Sijil ataupun Diploma dalam program TVET yang berkemahiran tinggi. Selain itu, bagi pelajar yang kurang kecenderungan dalam akademik dan remaja di luar sistem pendidikan terdapat juga program khas Sijil dan Sistem Latihan Dual Nasional (SLDN).' => 'In general, there are two routes to enter the TVET field, namely through the Malaysian Certificate of Education (SPM) or Form 3 Assessment (PT3). SPM graduates have the opportunity to continue their studies either in the field of Certificate or Diploma in the highly skilled TVET program. In addition, for students who are less inclined in academics and teenagers outside the education system there is also a special National Dual Certificate and Training System (SLDN) program.',
    'Kelayakan minimum bagi memasuki institusi TVET?' => 'What are the minimum qualifications to enter a TVET institution?',
    'Kelayakan minimum bagi kemasukan ke institusi-institusi TVET adalah berdasarkan tawaran yang dikeluarkan kementerian/agensi yang melaksanakan program.' => 'The minimum qualification for admission to TVET institutions is based on the offer issued by the ministry/agency implementing the program.',
    'Apakah keistimewaan yang diperolehi apabila menyambung pelajaran dalam bidang TVET?' => 'What are the privileges obtained when continuing studies in the field of TVET?',
    'Lulusan program TVET mampu menguasai pengetahuan dan kemahiran praktikal dengan lebih baik berbanding lulusan program akademik. Kelebihan ini berpotensi untuk membuka lebih banyak peluang pekerjaan dan menarik minat majikan untuk menawarkan pekerjaan kepada lulusan TVET.' => 'TVET program graduates are able to master knowledge and practical skills better than academic program graduates. This advantage has the potential to open up more job opportunities and attract employers to offer jobs to TVET graduates.',
    'Kembali ke TVET' => 'Back to TVET',
    'Program Kolej Vokasional Ambilan 2021 Bintulu' => 'Ambilan Vocational College Program 2021 Bintulu',
    'Kolej Vokasional Bintulu' => 'Bintulu Vocational College',
    'Info Program' => 'Program Info',
    'Kosmetologi' => 'Cosmetology',
    'Program ini mendedahkan murid kepada penjagaan dan rawatan wajah dan anggota badan, penggayaan rambut, seni make-up, refleksologi serta amalan kesihatan dan kebersihan, pengurusan dan pengoperasian salon.' => 'This program exposes students to face and body care and treatment, hair styling, make-up art, reflexology as well as health and hygiene practices, salon management and operation.',
    'Seni Kulinari' => 'Culinary Art',
    'Program ini mendedahkan murid kepada operasi dan penyelenggaraan dapur, penyediaan makanan dan restoran, penyediaan pencuci mulut, masakan Timur dan Barat, kuih tempatan, roti, pasteri dan manisan, seni makanan, penyediaan makanan halal dan pengurusan makanan.' => 'This program exposes students to kitchen operations and maintenance, food and restaurant preparation, dessert preparation, Eastern and Western cuisine, local cakes, bread, pastries and sweets, food art, halal food preparation and food management.',
    'Seni Reka Fesyen' => 'Fashion Design Art',
    'Program ini menyediakan murid tentang jenis, klasifikasi dan alatan jahitan serta fabrik dan tekstil, memberi pendedahan tentang aliran bagi pakaian yang berkualiti serta bersesuaian dengan tema dan kegunaan pasaran tempatan dan antarabangsa mengikut fesyen terkini.' => 'This program provides students with the types, classifications and tools of sewing as well as fabrics and textiles, giving exposure to trends for quality clothing that is compatible with the themes and uses of the local and international markets according to the latest fashion.',
    'Teknologi Automotif' => 'Automotive Technology',
    'Program ini memberi pendedahan asas enjin kenderaan bagi menimbulkan minat murid supaya bersedia dan berusaha untuk melanjutkan pembelajaran ke peringkat tertinggi dalam bidang automotif, menjadi modal insan yang berkemahiran dan dapat menyumbang ke arah pembangunan negara.' => "This program provides exposure to the basics of vehicle engines to arouse students' interest so that they are prepared and strive to continue learning to the highest level in the automotive field, becoming skilled human capital and able to contribute towards the development of the country.",
    'Teknologi Elektrik' => 'Electric technology',
    'Program ini menyediakan murid kepada sistem kuasa, arus (DC & AC), penyelenggaraan, pemasangan dan menguji elektrik domestik dan industri, kawalan motor, sengaraan kejuruteraan, melukis dan mentafsir litar serta memahami akta elektrikal dan peraturan pemasangan yang ditetapkan.' => 'This program prepares students for power systems, current (DC & AC), maintenance, installation and testing of domestic and industrial electricity, motor control, engineering maintenance, drawing and interpreting circuits and understanding electrical acts and installation regulations.',
    'Teknologi Elektronik' => 'Electronic technology',
    'Program ini memberi penekanan kepada mentafsir dan mengenalpasti simbol, komponen dan lukisan skematik, memahami, menguji dan mengira litar, prinsip kejuruteraan elektronik, pemasangan dan penyelenggaraan sistem audio dan video, digital, elektronik kuasa, sistem kawalan, sistem komunikasi dan industri robotik.' => 'The program emphasizes interpreting and identifying symbols, components and schematic drawings, understanding, testing and calculating circuits, principles of electronic engineering, installation and maintenance of audio and video systems, digital, power electronics, control systems, communication systems and industrial robotics.',
    'Teknologi Kimpalan' => 'Welding technology',
    'Program ini menyediakan murid kepada kimpalan mengikut aras bs/aws, proses dan teknik, pengkelasan bahan logam, teknik. Tata cara serta teknik pemotongan mekanikal dan haba, lukisan kejuruteraan, fabrikasi, pemasangan kimpal paku dan kimpal arka logam berperisai. Di samping itu, murid juga didedahkan dengan automasi komputer.' => 'This program prepares students for welding according to bs/aws level, processes and techniques, classification of metal materials, techniques. Mechanical and thermal cutting procedures and techniques, engineering drawings, fabrication, stud welding and shielded metal arc welding. In addition, students are also exposed to computer automation.',
    'Teknologi Pembinaan' => 'Construction technology',
    'Program ini memperkenalkan murid kepada asas pembinaan sesuatu struktur. Murid akan didedahkan dengan bahan-bahan binaan, caracara asas pembinaan, asas lukisan pelan, keselamatan industri, asas kejuruteraan elektrik dan elektronik, pengurusan industri' => 'This program introduces students to the basics of building a structure. Students will be exposed to building materials, basic construction methods, basic plan drawing, industrial safety, basic electrical and electronic engineering, industrial management',
    'Teknologi Pemesinan Industri' => 'Industrial Machining Technology',
    'Program ini menawarkan pendedahan kepada amalan bengkel pemesinan industri, lukisan teknikal dan geometri, rekabentuk pembuatan terbantu komputer, mengenalpasti jenis, senarai alatan dan pengoperasian mesin industri.' => 'This program offers exposure to industrial machining workshop practices, technical and geometric drawing, computer aided manufacturing design, identifying types, tool lists and operating industrial machines.',
    'Penerangan Bidang' => 'Field Description',
    'Bidang vokasional memberikan peluang kepada pelajar yang berpencapaian baik atau sederhana dalam akademik dan berminat kepada pembelajaran bercorak vokasional (berkaitan pekerjaan).  Isi kandungan bidang vokasional mempunyai komponen teori dan praktikal yang seimbang. Objektif aliran ini adalah untuk membantu melahirkan separa profesional (juruteknik/pembantu teknik) dalam bidang kejuruteraan dan bukan kejuruteraan. Setelah tamat pengajian, murid berpeluang ke IPTA, IPTS, dan institut latihan kemahiran awam dan swasta, atau terus ke alam pekerjaan.' => 'Vocational fields provide opportunities for students who achieve well or moderately in academics and are interested in vocational (job-related) patterned learning. The content of the vocational field has a balanced theoretical and practical component. The objective of this stream is to help produce semi-professionals (technicians/technical assistants) in engineering and non-engineering fields. After graduation, students have the opportunity to go to IPTA, IPTS, and public and private skills training institutes, or directly into the world of work.',
    'Program ini merangkumi dua (2) tahun pengajian di peringkat Sijil dan dua (2) tahun 6  (6) bulan di peringkat Diploma (termasuk lima (5) bulan On The Job Training)' => 'This program includes two (2) years of study at the Certificate level and two (2) years and 6 (6) months at the Diploma level (including five (5) months of On The Job Training)',
    'Murid yang berjaya di peringkat Sijil akan dianugerahkan Sijil Vokasional Malaysia (SVM)' => 'Students who are successful at the Certificate level will be awarded the Malaysian Vocational Certificate (SVM)',
    'Murid yang dianugerahkan SVM dan melepasi syarat kemasukan layak menyambung pengajian di peringkat Diploma di Kolej Vokasional yang sama' => 'Pupils who are awarded SVM and pass the entry requirements are eligible to continue their studies at the Diploma level at the same Vocational College',
    'Murid yang tidak melepasi syarat kemasukan ke peringkat Diploma akan menyambung pengajian di Kolej Vokasional yang sama dalam bidang kemahiran dan dianugerahkan Sijil Kemahiran Malaysia (SKM) berdasarkan tahap kompetensi yang dicapai' => 'Students who do not pass the entry requirements for the Diploma level will continue their studies at the same Vocational College in the same field of skills and be awarded the Malaysian Skills Certificate (SKM) based on the level of competence achieved',
    'Murid yang lulus pengajian di peringkat Diploma akan dianugerahkan Diploma oleh Senat Kolej Vokasional, Kementerian Pendidikan Malaysia' => 'Students who pass their studies at the Diploma level will be awarded a Diploma by the Vocational College Senate, Ministry of Education Malaysia',
    'Matlamat Program Kolej Vokasional untuk melahirkan tenaga kerja yang mahir dan kompeten bagi memenuhi keperluan industri dan entrepreneur' => 'The goal of the Vocational College Program is to produce a skilled and competent workforce to meet the needs of industry and entrepreneurs',
    'Sekolah Pendidikan Khas' => 'Special Education School',
    'Program Pendidikan Khas Integrasi' => 'Integration Special Education Program',
    'Program Pendidikan Inklusif' => 'Inclusive Education Program',
    'Pendidikan Islam Dalam Pendidikan Khas' => 'Islamic Education in Special Education',
    'Pusat Perkhidmatan Pendidikan Khas (3PK)' => 'Special Education Service Center (3PK)',
    'Rancangan Pendidikan Individu' => 'Individual Education Plan',
    'Pusat Sumber Bahagian Pendidikan Khas' => 'Special Education Division Resource Center',
    'Pendidikan Khas' => 'Special Education',
    'Sekolah Pendidikan Khas adalah sekolah yang menyediakan pendidikan khas bagi murid berkeperluan khas (MBK) pada semua peringkat persekolahan. Sekolah Pendidikan Khas ini dikendalikan terus oleh Bahagian Pendidikan Khas (BPKhas).' => 'Special Education School is a school that provides special education for students with special needs (MBK) at all levels of schooling. This Special Education School is managed directly by the Special Education Division (BPKhas).',
    'Senarai sekolah yang mempunyai pendidikan khas di Bintulu adalah seperti berikut:' => 'The list of schools with special education in Bintulu is as follows:',
    'BIL.' => 'NO.',
    'NAMA SEKOLAH' => 'SCHOOL NAME',
    'ALAMAT' => 'ADDRESS',
    'EMEL [@moe.edu.my]' => 'EMAIL [@moe.edu.my]',
    'NO. TELEFON' => 'PHONE NO.',
    'Kembali ke Pendidikan Khas' => 'Back to Special Education',
    'Sejarah' => 'History',
    'Tahun 1962- Program Pendidikan Khas Integrasi (PPKI) (Rancangan Percantuman) bagi pendidikan kanak-kanak kurang upaya penglihatan di sekolah rendah dan menegah arus perdana yang terpilih mula diperkenalkan.' => 'Year 1962 - The Special Education Program for Integration (PPKI) (Integration Plan) for the education of visually impaired children in primary schools and preventing the selected mainstream was first introduced.',
    'Tahun 1963- Pembukaan kelas-kelas pendidikan khas Rancangan Percantuman kurang upaya pendengaran di sekolah rendah dan sekolah menengah mula dilaksanakan.' => 'Year 1963- The opening of special education classes for the Hearing Impaired Integration Plan in primary and secondary schools began to be implemented.',
    'Tahun 1988- Kementerian Pendidikan Malaysia telah memulakan kelas perintis untuk murid-murid peringkat rendah bermasalah pembelajaran dan seterusnya ke suluruh Negara.' => 'Year 1988 - The Malaysian Ministry of Education started a pilot class for primary school students with learning disabilities and continued throughout the country.',
    'Tujuan Program' => 'Purpose of the Program',
    'Semua murid berkeperluan pendidikan Khas (MBK) berpeluang untuk menerima akses pendidikan yang releven dan sesuai' => 'All students with Special Educational Needs (SED) have the opportunity to receive access to relevant and appropriate education',
    'Semua MBK perlu diperkembangkan bakat dan potensi murid melalui pendidikan vokasional bagi menghasilkan insan yang berkemahiran ke arah meningkatkan kualiti hidup.' => 'All MBK need to develop the talent and potential of students through vocational education to produce skilled people towards improving the quality of life.',
    'Semua MBK diberi peluang untuk mengikuti Program Intervensi Awal agar tahap keupayaan mereka dapat dioptimumkan.' => 'All MBK are given the opportunity to follow the Early Intervention Program so that their ability level can be optimized.',
    'Menyediakan peluang MBK untuk mengikuti program pendidikan yang menjurus kepada peningkatan potensi sedia ada bagi melahirkan kumpulan separuh mahir dan seterusnya menjadi aset kepada negara.' => 'Providing opportunities for MBK to follow educational programs aimed at increasing the existing potential to produce a semi-skilled group and subsequently become an asset to the country.',
    'MBK yang berpotensi seboleh-bolehnya ditempatkan secara inklusif di kelas-kelas arus perdana..' => 'MBK who have the potential to be placed as inclusively as possible in mainstream classes..',
    'Peranan BPKHAS' => 'The role of BPKHAS',
    'Bahagian Pendidikan Khas berperanan merancang, mengurus dan mengawal selia pembangunan pendidikan bagi MBK di peringkat Kementerian.' => 'The Special Education Division is responsible for planning, managing and regulating educational development for MBK at the Ministry level.',
    'Peranan Jabatan Pelajaran Negeri (JPN)' => 'The Role of the State Education Department (JPN)',
    'Jabatan Pelajaran Negeri (JPN) berperanan merancang dan mengurus PPKI, serta mengawal selia pelaksanaan pembangunan pendidikan bagi MBK di PPKI peringkat negeri.' => 'The State Education Department (JPN) has the role of planning and managing PPKI, as well as regulating the implementation of educational development for MBK in PPKI at the state level.',
    'Konsep Program' => 'Program Concept',
    'Konsep Program Pendidikan Inklusif (PPI) adalah selaras dengan penyataan dalam Peraturan - peraturan Pendidikan (Pendidikan Khas) 2013 seperti di bawah : ' => 'The concept of the Inclusive Education Program (PPI) is in line with the statement in the Education (Special Education) Regulations 2013 as below : ',
    '"Program Pendidikan Inklusif" ertinya suatu program pendidikan bagi murid berkeperluan pendidikan khas yang dihadiri oleh murid berkeperluan khas bersama-sama dengan murid lain dalam kelas yang sama di sekolah kerajaan atau sekolah bantuan kerajaan.' => '"Inclusive Education Program" means an educational program for students with special educational needs attended by students with special needs together with other students in the same class in a government school or a government aided school.',
    'Meningkatkan penyertaan dan memberi peluang kepada MBK mengikuti program akademik dan bukan akademik bersama-sama murid di arus perdana. PPI juga memberi kesedaran kepada masyarakat supaya tidak menafikan potensi MBK dan percaya bahawa ketidakupayaan mereka boleh diminimakan jika diberi peluang yang sama.' => 'Increase participation and give MBK students the opportunity to follow academic and non-academic programs together with students in the mainstream. PPI also gives awareness to the community not to deny the potential of MBK and believe that their disability can be minimized if given the same opportunity.',
    'Pendekatan Program' => 'Program Approach',
    'Inklusif Penuh' => 'Full Inclusive',
    'MBK belajar secara sepenuh masa bersama-sama murid arus perdana. MBK mengikuti pembelajaran bagi semua mata pelajaran akademik berasaskan kurikulum kebangsaan atau kurikulum kebangsaan yang diubahsuai dengan bantuan atau tanpa bantuan perkhidmatan sokongan.' => 'MBK studies full-time alongside mainstream students. MBK follows learning for all academic subjects based on the national curriculum or a modified national curriculum with or without the help of support services.',
    'Inklusif Separa' => 'Partially Inclusive',
    'MBK belajar bersama-sama murid arus perdana bagi mata pelajaran akademik atau aktiviti koakademik atau aktiviti kokurikulum tertentu sahaja mengikut keupayaan mereka. MBK yang mengikuti inklusif separa bagi mata pelajaran akademik berasaskan kurikulum kebangsaan atau kurikulum kebangsaan yang diubahsuai dengan sedikit atau tanpa bantuan perkhidmatan sokongan. Inklusif separa bagi aktiviti koakademik atau kokurikulum adalah berdasarkan potensi, bakat dan keupayaan mereka.' => 'MBK studies together with mainstream students for academic subjects or co-academic activities or specific co-curricular activities only according to their ability. MBK that follows partial inclusion of academic subjects based on the national curriculum or a modified national curriculum with little or no assistance from support services. Partial inclusion of co-academic or co-curricular activities is based on their potential, talent and ability.',
    'Program j-QAF Pendidikan Khas adalah suatu usaha memperkasakan Pendidikan Islam (PI) di Pendidikan Khas untuk :' => 'The j-QAF Special Education Program is an effort to empower Islamic Education (PI) in Special Education to :',
    'Murid Berkeperluan Khas (MBK) Bermasalah Pembelajaran, Bermasalah Pendengaran dan Bermasalah Penglihatan.' => 'Students with Special Needs (MBK) with learning problems, hearing problems and vision problems.',
    'Bagi Murid Bermasalah Pembelajaran program ini memberi penekanan khusus dalam:' => 'For students with learning difficulties, this program places special emphasis on:',
    "Pengajaran dan Pembelajaran al-Quran menggunakan Modul Kaedah Iqra' dan" => "Teaching and Learning the Qur'an using the Iqra' Method Module and",
    'Pengajaran dan Pembelajaran Fardhu Ain menggunakan Modul Amali Solat.' => 'Teaching and Learning Fardhu Ain using the Practical Prayer Module.',
    'Bagi Murid Bermasalah Pendengaran program ini memberi penekanan khusus dalam:' => 'For Hearing Impaired Students, this program places special emphasis on:',
    "Pengajaran dan Pembelajaran al-Quran menggunakan Modul Kaedah Iqra'," => "Teaching and Learning the Quran using the Iqra' Method Module,",
    'Pengajaran dan Pembelajaran Fardhu Ain menggunakan Modul Amali Solat, dan' => 'Teaching and Learning Fardhu Ain using the Practical Prayer Module, and',
    'Pengajaran dan Pembelajaran Jawi menggunakan Modul Pembelajaran Jawi.' => 'Teaching and Learning Javanese using the Javanese Learning Module.',
    'Manakala bagi Murid Bermasalah Penglihatan menggunakan sepenuh modul j-QAF aliran perdana yang dilaksanakan di peringkat sekolah rendah.' => 'While for Visually Impaired Pupils using the full mainstream j-QAF module implemented at the primary school level.',
    'Pusat Perkhidmatan Pendidikan Khas (3PK) merupakan pusat khidmat setempat yang menyediakan perkhidmatan sokongan berbentuk intervensi, rehabilitasi, dan konsultasi dalam bidang khusus iaitu Audiologi, Psikologi, Patologi Pertuturan Bahasa, Terapi Carakerja, dan Peripatetik.' => 'The Special Education Center (3PK) is a local service center that provides support services in the form of intervention, rehabilitation, and consultation in specific fields such as Audiology, Psychology, Speech Language Pathology, Occupational Therapy, and Peripatetics.',
    'Sokongan 3PK bertujuan meminimakan impak ketidakupayaan Murid Berkeperluan Khas (MBK) bagi membolehkan MBK menjalani proses pembelajaran dengan lebih baik selain membimbing MBK ke arah hidup berdikari serta bermakna.' => '3PK support aims to minimize the impact of the disability of Special Needs Students (SES) to enable SES to go through the learning process better as well as guide SES towards an independent and meaningful life.',
    'Pengurusan 3PK negeri berada di bawah seliaan Cawangan Latihan dan Khidmat Bantu (CLKB), Bahagian Pendidikan Khas, Kementerian Pendidikan Malaysia. Terdapat 12 buah 3PK di seluruh Malaysia yang beroperasi di Sekolah Pendidikan Khas dan satu (1) beroperasi di Bahagian Pendidikan Khas.' => 'State 3PK management is under the supervision of the Training and Support Services Branch (CLKB), Special Education Division, Ministry of Education Malaysia. There are 12 3PK throughout Malaysia operating in Special Education Schools and one (1) operating in the Special Education Division.',
    'Terapi Carakerja JOCV' => 'JOCV Occupational Therapy',
    'Peranan Dan Fungsi Pusat Perkhidmatan Pendidikan Khas (3PK)' => 'The Role and Function of the Special Education Service Center (3PK)',
    'Melaksanakan program saringan kepada murid yang mempunyai ciri-ciri berkeperluan khas.' => 'Implement a screening program for students with special needs characteristics.',
    'Melaksanakan ujian/penilaian dengan menggunakan peralatan khas/instrumen standard bagi mengenal pasti masalah-masalah spesifik yang dihadapi oleh kanak-kanak dan MBK.' => 'Carry out tests/assessments using special equipment/standard instruments to identify specific problems faced by children and MBK.',
    'Melaksanakan program intervensi/rehabilitasi bagi meminimakan impak ketidakupayaan kanak-kanak dan MBK.' => "Implement intervention/rehabilitation programs to minimize the impact of children's disabilities and MBK.",
    'Melaksanakan program intervensi awal dari aspek domain-domain perkembangan bagi kesediaan kanak-kanak ke alam persekolahan.' => "Implement an early intervention program from the aspects of developmental domains for children's readiness for school.",
    'Menyediakan perkhidmatan konsultasi mengikut bidang khusus iaitu Peripatetik, Audiologi, Patalogi Pertuturan Bahasa, Terapi Carakerja, dan Psikologi bagi menyokong pendidikan MBK secara menyeluruh.' => 'Provide consultation services according to specific fields such as Peripatetics, Audiology, Speech Language Pathology, Occupational Therapy, and Psychology to support MBK education as a whole.',
